AutoCloseable, ResultSet, Wrapper
public class AutoCloseResultSet
extends DelegatingResultSet<ResultSet>
implements AutoCloseable, ResultSet

An AutoCloseable ResultSet. When the automatic resource management block construct invokes close(), close() will be called on the underlying ResultSet.
